	(@BuletteStandingLeapId, 'The bulette''s long jump is up to 30 feet and its high jump is up to 15 feet, with or without a running start.'),
	(@CentaurChargeId, 'If the centaur moves at least 30 feet straight toward a target and then hits it with a pike attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra 10 (3d6) piercing damage.'),
	(@ChuulAmphibiousId, 'The chuul can breathe air and water.'),
	(@ChuulSenseMagicId, 'The chuul senses magic within 120 feet of it at will. This trait otherwise works like the detect magic spell but isn''t itself magical.'),
	(@CloakerDamageTransferId, 'While attached to a creature, the cloaker takes only half the damage dealt to it (rounded down), and that creature takes the other half.'),
