	(@WarhorseTramplingChargeId, 'If the horse moves at least 20 feet straight toward a creature and then hits it with a hooves attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 14 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the horse can make another attack with its hooves against it as a bonus action.'),
	(@WeaselKeenHearingAndSmellId, 'The weasel has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on hearing or smell.'),
