	(@SpySneakAttackId, 'Once per turn, the spy deals an extra 7 (2d6) damage when it hits a target with a weapon attack and has advantage on the attack roll, or when the target is within 5 feet of an ally of the spy that isn''t incapacitated and the spy doesn''t have disadvantage on the attack roll.'),
